data.description: This recently remodeled home  embodies the unique charm and character of the Southwest, coupled with modern comfort and convenience. Open floor plan connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a sense of spaciousness and flow. Large windows throughout. The den can be used as an office, gym or an extra  gathering area.If you're looking for a serene and welcoming home in Tucson, this property is a must-see. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!
